NPC Archetypes
The world is deliberately timeless and anachronistic — characters know what technology, the internet, and modern culture are. They exist in a weird liminal gothic town outside of normal time. Monty talks about games and tech naturally. Eleanor has heard of the internet but it made her feel worse. Cassius finds technology beneath him. Creed is suspicious of it. Gerald checks online community boards obsessively. Aldous has a ledger app AND a physical ledger. Marta has stalked Agnes on social media.

