5. AI Conversation System
How It Works
Each door encounter is powered by the Claude API. The player's typed dialogue is sent with a system prompt that defines the NPC's personality, hidden desire, current emotional state, and running suspicion/warmth levels. The API returns a structured JSON response every turn.

JSON Response Format
{ "reply": "...", "suspicion": 2, "warmth": 4, "dealAccepted": false, "slamDoor": false }

Field
Type
Description
reply
String
What the NPC says out loud in the encounter
suspicion
Int 0-10
How suspicious the NPC is becoming of the player
warmth
Int 0-10
How receptive the NPC is to the player's pitch
dealAccepted
Boolean
Whether the NPC accepted the deal on this turn
slamDoor
Boolean
Whether the NPC immediately ends the conversation


System Prompt Contents Per NPC
Name, age, occupation, and personality type
Their hidden desire — what they want most in the world
Current emotional state and life circumstances
Religious and moral values — affects how easily they are swayed
Running suspicion and warmth values updated each turn
Instruction to respond only in valid JSON with no preamble or markdown


6. The Church Investigator
Suspicion Meter
A town-wide suspicion meter fills based on player actions. As it crosses thresholds the Investigator escalates his behavior.

Suspicion Level
Investigator Behavior
0-25%
Dormant — not yet spawned, town is calm
25-50%
Spawns and begins casual patrol around town
50-75%
Actively interviews NPCs near houses the player has visited
75-100%
Hunting mode — moves faster, wider interview radius, near end state


What Raises Suspicion
Successfully completing a deal with any NPC
A Regretting NPC being interviewed by the Investigator
A Suspicious NPC tattling after being approached
Time passing naturally — suspicion creeps up even with no action

What Lowers Suspicion
Fulfilled NPCs actively misleading the Investigator during interviews
Using a Silence ability on a Regretting NPC before they are interviewed
Offering a deal to the Investigator himself — extremely high risk, very high reward


