Dual-view system — top-down overworld and first-person encounter
AI-powered NPC dialogue via Claude API with structured JSON responses
3 deal types: Wealth, Love, Revenge
Church Investigator with patrol and basic interview behavior
Town-wide suspicion meter with escalation thresholds
Win and lose condition

Future Scope
